node.text: I had the pleasure of talking to Maisy about voting, the environment and her pop Joe the other day! If you haven’t voted already, visit iwillvote.com to make a plan to do so!!!! Making your voice heard, even if you are like me and not of voting age, is important today and everyday. ❤️❤️❤️❤️

node.text: used to go to amoeba all the time as a tween to touch all the records and dream about what my own would look and feel like. yesterday I got to find out! been the coolest experience seeing the SOUR vinyl out in the world. thank u all for buying & listening. it means soooo much💜🖤💜🖤

node.text: SOUR vinyl comes out this Friday and I couldn’t be more excited if I tried!!!!!! u can preorder them now on oliviarodrigo.com if ya like! I’ve discovered so many of my favorite albums through vinyl records and it’s the coolest thing in the world to get to hold one with songs I wrote. august 20th mark your cals!!!!🎸💔💜💕🍓🔪🫀🪐❤️‍🔥🖤🦋
